metadata.exif:ImageDescription: Abu Hajil, South Central Iraq, 5/15/3 - Iraqis uncover a vast mass grave for Iraqi Shias executed after the 1991 uprising against Saddam Hussien. Thousands of decomposed bodies, many of them soldiers, were exhumed to be claimed by despondent family members. Photo by Benjamin Lowy/Corbis
